Rudraksh.  - Tolong, Preesha.

00:16:42.787 --> 00:16:43.867
Apa yang saya lakukan?

00:16:44.547 --> 00:16:45.987
Bagaimana cara membuat
Rudraksh mengerti?

00:16:46.027 --> 00:16:47.947
